          "source_html": "<div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"><strong>Questions 14 - 18</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">Look at the six paragraphs </span><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"><strong>(A - F)</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">. Which paragraph contains the following information?</span></p><p><br/></p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"matrix-container\">\r\n        <table>\r\n            <thead><tr><th class=\"corner-header\">Question / Paragraph</th><th>A</th><th>B</th><th>C</th><th>D</th><th>E</th><th>F</th><th>G</th></tr></thead>\r\n            <tbody>\r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">14</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>14</strong> similarities between studies of mammoth remains from different parts of the world</p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_14\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q14\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_14\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q14\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_14\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q14\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_14\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q14\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_14\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q14\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_14\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q14\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_14\" value=\"G\" data-zyz-question=\"q14\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"8\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：D</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键信息: “similarities”和“studies of mammoth”</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: D段，“Most of these came from the Great Lakes region of North America, and his research showed that these animals continued to thrive, despite the late Pleistocene* temperature change. On the other hand, to Fisher the tusks often revealed telltale evidence of human hunting. His samples frequently came from animals that had died in the autumn, when they should have been attheir peak after summer grazing, and less likely to die of natural causes, but also when humans would have been most eager to stockpile meat for the coming winter. He has done limited work in Siberia, but his analysis of tusks from Wrangel Island, off the coast of Siberia, suggests the same conclusion.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文提到Fisher对北美和西伯利亚的研究得出了相似的结论。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：different parts of the world =Wrangel Island；&nbsp;mammoth remains=tusks</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">15</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>15</strong> details of the uses to which mammoth body parts were put</p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_15\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q15\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_15\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q15\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_15\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q15\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_15\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q15\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_15\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q15\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_15\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q15\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_15\" value=\"G\" data-zyz-question=\"q15\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"8\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：B</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键信息: “uses”和“mammoth body parts”。</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: B段，“In addition to exploiting mammoths for food, they used their bones and tusks to make weapons, tools, and even dwellings.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文详细说明了猛犸的身体部位被用于制作武器、工具和房屋。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：mammoth body parts=&nbsp;bones and tusks</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">16</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>16</strong> a theory that accounts for the damage to Lyuba&#39;s face</p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_16\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q16\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_16\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q16\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_16\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q16\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_16\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q16\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_16\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q16\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_16\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q16\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_16\" value=\"G\" data-zyz-question=\"q16\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"8\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：E</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键信息: “theory”和“damage to Lyuba&#39;s face”</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: E段，“In fact, the sediment in Lyuba&#39;s trunk was packed so tightly that Fisher saw it as a possible explanation for the dent above her trunk. If she was frantically fighting for breath and inhaled convulsively, perhaps a partial vacuum was created in the base of her trunk, which would have flattened surrounding soft tissue. To Fisher, the circumstances of Lyuba&#39;s death were clear: she had asphyxiated. Suzuki, however, proposed a different interpretation, seeing more evidence for drowning than asphyxiation.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文提供了对Lyuba脸部损伤的两种解释。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：damage= dent</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">17</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>17</strong> an explanation of how an individual was able to identify a small corpse</p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_17\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q17\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_17\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q17\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_17\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q17\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_17\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q17\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_17\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q17\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_17\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q17\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_17\" value=\"G\" data-zyz-question=\"q17\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"8\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：A</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键信息: “identify a small corpse”</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: A段，“<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Although he&#39;d never seen such an animal before, Khudi had seen many mammoth tusks, the thick corkscrew shafts that his people found each summer, and this persuaded him the corpse was a baby mammoth.</span>”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文解释了Khudi如何通过之前看到的猛犸象牙来识别出这是一只幼年猛犸象的尸体。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">18</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>18</strong> A comparison between Lyuba and other young mammoth corpses</p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_18\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q18\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_18\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q18\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_18\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q18\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_18\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q18\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_18\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q18\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_18\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q18\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55393_18\" value=\"G\" data-zyz-question=\"q18\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"8\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：C</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键信息:“comparison”和“Lyuba and other young mammoth corpses”</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: C段，“Fisher and Buigues had examined other specimens together, including infants, but these had been in a relatively poor state. Lyuba was another story entirely, other than the missing hair and toenails, the only flaw in her pristine appearance was a curious dent above the trunk.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文提到<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Fisher和Buigues将</span>Lyuba与其他猛犸的研究进行比较。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><br/></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">Questions 19-23</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">Choose the correct person </span><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"><strong>(A - G)</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"> for each statement. You may choose </span><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">any correct person</span><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"> more than once.</span></p><p><br/></p><p><strong>List of People</strong></p><p><strong>A</strong>&nbsp;Yuri Khudi</p><p><strong>B</strong>&nbsp;Kirill Serotetto</p><p><strong>C</strong>&nbsp;Adrian Lister</p><p><strong>D</strong>&nbsp;Alexei Tikhonov</p><p><strong>E</strong>&nbsp;Dan Fisher</p><p><strong>F</strong>&nbsp;Bernard Buigues</p><p><strong>G</strong>&nbsp;Naoki Suzuki</p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"matrix-container\">\r\n        <table>\r\n            <thead><tr><th class=\"corner-header\">Question / Paragraph</th><th>A</th><th>B</th><th>C</th><th>D</th><th>E</th><th>F</th><th>G</th></tr></thead>\r\n            <tbody>\r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">19</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>19</strong> The indications are that mammoths died as a result of climate change.</p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_19\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q19\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_19\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q19\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_19\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q19\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_19\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q19\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_19\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q19\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_19\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q19\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_19\" value=\"G\" data-zyz-question=\"q19\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"8\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：C</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键信息: Adrian Lister</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: B段，“&nbsp;We have strong evidence that the temperature rise played a significant part in their extinction.&#39; says Adrian Lister, a palaeontologist and mammoth expert at London&#39;s Natural History Museum.&#39;&nbsp;”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文提到Adrian Lister认为气温升高书导致猛犸象灭绝的重要原因之一，所以可以说气候变化导致了猛犸的灭绝。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：&nbsp;indications=evidence；climate change=temperature rise</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">20</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>20</strong> Teeth analysis is important in discovering why mammoths died out.</p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_20\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q20\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_20\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q20\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_20\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q20\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_20\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q20\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_20\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q20\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_20\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q20\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_20\" value=\"G\" data-zyz-question=\"q20\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"8\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：E</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键信息:&nbsp;Dan Fisher</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: F段，“Her good general health was shown in the record of her dental development, a confirmation for Fisher that dental research is useful for evaluating health and thus key to investigating the causes of mammoth extinction.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文提到Fisher通过牙齿分析研究猛犸的健康状况，从而探索灭绝的原因。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">21</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>21</strong> The corpse of the baby mammoth is in better condition than any other that has been discovered.</p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_21\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q21\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_21\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q21\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_21\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q21\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_21\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q21\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_21\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q21\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_21\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q21\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_21\" value=\"G\" data-zyz-question=\"q21\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"8\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：D</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键信息:&nbsp;&nbsp;Alexei Tikhonov</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: C段，“The body of the baby mammoth was eventually sent to the St Petersburg Zoological Museum in Russia. Alexei Tikhonov, the museum&#39;s director, was one of the first scientists to view the baby, a female. According to Tikhonov, Khudi had rescued &#39;the best preserved mammoth to come down to US from the Ice Age&#39;, and he gratefully named her Lyuba, after Khudi&#39;s wife.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文提到Tikhonov认为Khudi拯救的猛犸象尸体是保存最好的冰河时期迁徙到美国的猛犸象尸体。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：better condition = best preserved&nbsp;</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">22</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>22</strong> It would be a mistake to ignore the baby mammoth&#39;s discovery, because of its potential importance.</p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_22\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q22\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_22\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q22\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_22\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q22\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_22\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q22\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_22\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q22\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_22\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q22\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_22\" value=\"G\" data-zyz-question=\"q22\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"8\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：A</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键信息:Yuri Khudi</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: A段，“Khudi realised the find might be significant and he knew he couldn&#39;t just return home and forget all about it.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路:</p><p>Khudi意识到这个发现可能非常重要，他知道自己不能就这样回家，然后完全忘记这件事。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">23</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>23</strong> Mammoths often died at a time of year when they should have been in good physical condition.</p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_23\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q23\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_23\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q23\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_23\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q23\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_23\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q23\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_23\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q23\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_23\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q23\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_55515_23\" value=\"G\" data-zyz-question=\"q23\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"8\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：E</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键信息:Dan Fisher</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: D段，“His samples frequently came from animals that had died in the autumn, when they should have been at their peak after summer grazing, and less likely to die of natural causes, but also when humans would have been most eager to stockpile meat for the coming winter.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文提到Dan Fisher认为猛犸象在秋季死亡，而这个时期正是它们经过夏季放牧后身体应该处于最佳状态的时候。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"><strong>Questions 24 - 26</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">C</span><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">omplete the sentences. Write </span><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"><strong>NO MORE THAN TWO WORDS</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: MonospacedNumber, LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"> in each gap.</span></p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">24</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p>Some researchers say that a marked rise in temperature impacted on mammoths by changing the type of <span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q24\"></span> available.</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> <span class=\"ans-tag\">24</span> vegetation</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\">\r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 24</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>定位关键信息: “marked rise in temperature impacted”和“changing the type of”</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: B段，“<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Mammoths became extinct between 14,000 and 10,000 years ago and since the extinctions coincided with the end of the most recent Ice age, many researchers believe that the primary cause of the great die-off was&nbsp;</span>the sharp rise in temperature, which dramatically altered the vegetation.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文提到研究者认为猛犸象在最近的冰河时期末灭绝是因为气温上升改变了植被类型。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">marked rise=<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">sharp rise;&nbsp;<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">changing=<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">altered</span></span></span></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">25</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p>Fisher concluded that many of the mammoth tusks he looked at displayed signs of <span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q25\"></span>&nbsp;.</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> <span class=\"ans-tag\">25</span> human hunting</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\">\r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 25</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>定位关键信息: “Fisher”和“tusks”和“signs of”</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: D段，“&nbsp;On the other hand, to Fisher the tusks often revealed telltale evidence of human hunting.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文提到<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Fisher 认为</span>象牙显示了人类捕猎的迹象。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">displayed=<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">revealed；&nbsp;<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">signs=<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">evidence</span></span></span></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">26</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p>Not long after Lyuba’s death, the Mammuthus primigenius&nbsp;group she belonged to was replaced by another group that came from <span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q26\"></span> .</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> <span class=\"ans-tag\">26</span> North America</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\">\r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 26</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>定位关键信息: “after Lyuba&#39;s death”和“replaced by another group”</p><p><br/></p><p>对应原文: F段，“Analysis of her well-preserved DNA has revealed that she belonged to a distinct population of Mammuthus primigenius and that, soon after her time, another population migrating to Siberia from North America would take their place.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解题思路: 原文提到通过分析<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Lyuba保存完好的DNA，科学家确认</span>Lyuba所属的种群被<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">来自北美的群体所取代</span>。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">replaced by=<span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">take...place</span></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>",
